Text:
COVID isolation update:

Day 3 - just finished kicking off a Warnock zoom phone back; 

now watching livestream of my son’s hockey game which is being played at an arena with an awesome soundtrack - so far a lot of Van Halen, Ozzy, and, wait for it…Law and Order theme song.

Hey @brianschatz look who showed up in Connecticut today to campaign for @RepJahanaHayes! 

@CoryBooker!!

When are you coming to CT? https://t.co/4RlLRJqY3Y

This week we tried to convince Republicans, in the face of the end of Roe, to join us in increasing funds for contraception and family families. 

Republicans refused. 

@SenBlumenthal and I joined with Planned Parenthood today in Hartford to talk about it. https://t.co/0DjRF7U2WZ

Met so many interesting people in Watertown. #WalkCT 

Talked to:

- a pharmacist from Romania about natural medicine;
- a high school English teacher about politics in the classroom;
- a restaurant owner about COVID relief programs; 
- a mom about school based mental health. https://t.co/Bd9mwZulQq

Our friend @brianschatz has raised millions on Twitter for Dem candidates. Now it’s time to help him. 

Brian’s a climate leader, a super good guy, and up for re-election.

@CoryBooker and I hope you can help our friend. $50. $25. $10. Whatever you can do. https://t.co/vqlbpBmZJm

Going to college shouldn't force high level athletes into poverty just because the college sports machine has gotten addicted to making billions off their free labor. 

@LoriTrahanMA and I have a bill to right this wrong.
https://t.co/lFWHR7sjQs

Good news: we’re at $20,633 for @ReverendWarnock. 

@brianschatz @JasonKander @ossoff do you think we can kick this up to $30K by midnight?

Remember - to GROW our majority beyond 50, we need to HOLD tough seats like GA. Plus, Rafael is amazing!

How is it ok that:

- 90% of the country;
- the majority of the Senate;
- the majority of the House;
- and the President of the United States 

support comprehensive background checks... 

...but the rules of our democracy don't allow it to pass?

This is huge. ⁦

@tammybaldwin⁩ and I begged and begged the Trump Administration to use the Defense Production Act to address the pandemic. Trump refused. 

Biden is now using the DPA to dramatically ramp up vaccine production.   https://t.co/ZTDgeP0eJz
